# 🍕 Power BI Pizza Sales Analysis

This project presents an interactive Power BI dashboard to analyze pizza sales data.  
It provides insights into order patterns, most popular pizzas, sales by category, and customer preferences.

---

## 📊 Dashboard Screenshot

![Pizza Sales Dashboard](images/pizza_dashboard.png)

---

## 🔎 Key Insights
- **Most Ordered Pizza:** Veggie Small (veggie_veg_s)  
- **Sales by Size:** Large pizzas dominate sales, followed by Medium.  
- **Category Sales:** Veggie and Classic pizzas lead in revenue.  
- **Trend Analysis:** Orders remain consistent throughout the month, with spikes on certain days.  

---

## 🛠 Tools Used
- **Power BI** – Dashboard creation & visualization  
- **Excel/CSV** – Source data cleaning  
- **Data Analysis** – Sales trend insights

